] event held by Absolute Championship Berkut on November 13, 2015 at the Sukharev Sport Complex in [[Perm, Russia]]. \n\n===Results===\n{| class=\"wikitable\" style=\"font-size: 80%;\"\n|-\n! colspan=\"8\" style=\"background-color: #ccf; color: #000080; text-align: center;\" | '''Fight Card'''\n|-\n! colspan=\"1\" style=\"background-color: #E6E8FA; color: #000000; text-align: center;\" | Weight Class\n! colspan=\"1\" style=\"background-color: #E6E8FA; color: #000000; text-align: center;\" | \n! colspan=\"1\" style=\"background-color: #E6E8FA; color: #000000; text-align: center;\" | \n! colspan=\"1\" style=\"background-color: #E6E8FA; color: #000000; text-align: center;\" | \n! colspan=\"1\" style=\"background-color: #E6E8FA; color: #000000; text-align: center;\" | Method\n! colspan=\"1\" style=\"background-color: #E6E8FA; color: #000000; text-align: center;\" | Round  \n! colspan=\"1\" style=\"background-color: #E6E8FA; color: #000000; text-align: center;\" | Notes\n \n|-\n|KB Lightweight 70&nbsp;kg\n|{{flagicon|RUS}} Saifullah Hambahadov\n|def.\n|{{flagicon|RUS}} Kazbek Zubayrayev\n|Decision (Unanimous) \n|align=center|3\n|Grand Prix Final \n|-\n|KB Bantamweight 61&nbsp;kg\n|{{flagicon|SER}} Alexandar Konovalov \n|def.\n|{{flagicon|RUS}} Yakub Bersanukaev          \n|KO (Punch) \n|align=center|1\n|Grand Prix Final\n|-\n|KB Lightweight 70&nbsp;kg\n|{{flagicon|RUS}} Maxim Smirnov\n|def.\n|{{flagicon|DEN}} Rhassan Muhareb          \n|Decision (Unanimous) \n|align=center|3\n|\n|-\n|KB Welterweight 77&nbsp;kg\n|{{flagicon|MAR}} Zakaria Baitar  \n|def.\n|{{flagicon|RUS}} [[Alexander Stetsurenko]]          \n|TKO (Punches) \n|align=center|1\n|\n|-\n|KB Welterweight 77&nbsp;kg\n|{{flagicon|AZE}} [[Alim Nabiev]] \n|def.\n|{{flagicon|NED}} Masoud Rahimi          \n|Decision (Unanimous) \n|align=center|3\n|\n|-\n|KB Catchweight 86&nbsp;kg\n|{{flagicon|LAT}} Artem Mirontsev\n|def.\n|{{flagicon|RUS}} Renat Akhmetov       \n|Decision (Unanimous)\n|align=center|3\n|\n|-\n|KB Catc